      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm studying for my physics midterm and I'm a bit stuck on the concept of quantum entanglement. Can you give me a concise, non-mathematical summary of what it actually is and how it differs from just regular classical correlation? thanks",
      "source": "evaluator"
