    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "right, so it's basically about how it breaks our normal rules of how things work. is there any way to actually test if it's just hidden information we don't see yet, or is it actually as \"spooky\" as it sounds? like, is there some kind of hidden mechanism behind it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
